{"tid":759451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來依家屋企有樓都無用，要層樓實實在在有你名先得。","createTime":"2018-07-28T15:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T16:40:28.000Z","uid":35178,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b49488c4215e84a93918814c8b019dd51fceb56","tid":759451,"uid":35178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"話說今日同Uncle食飯，佢問起我屋企情況。<br />\n<br />\nUncle=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nUncle：係呢，近年樓市咁勁，有無話有咩Plan第日上樓？<br />\n<br />\n我：父母幫我準備好哂架喇，幫下我首期同幫下我供咁。（其實父母幫手Full Pay都得，不過廢事講太多。）<br />\n<br />\nUncle：即係依家父母仲未有確實話第日點幫你？<br />\n<br />\n我：（心諗：點撚樣同父母講，喂屌你老母，比住幾球買樓先）到時父母識做會幫手架啦。<br />\n<br />\nUncle：咁都唔係好穩陣姐。<br />\n<br />\n我：（爬飯算，唔知點應）<br />\n<br />\n廿頭出身你想我點撚樣買樓啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84e7bf569b6bb6c3a6300a251fbde3f6d50cee4","tid":759451,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"a3096605c7f6db600355ef07a39d6a1fb28a752c","tid":759451,"uid":38648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T16:40:28.000Z","msg":"55"}]}